{"lemma":"طَعْمُ","slug":"طَعْمُ","root":"ط.ع.م","root_slug":"ط-ع-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ط-ع-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"طَعْم","root":"طعم","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":11},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n26732","n26733","n26734","n26735"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B7%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%92%D9%85%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to eat","examples":[{"text":"قُل لَا أَجِدُ فِي مَا أُوحِيَ إِلَيَّ مُحَرَّمًا عَلَىٰ طَاعِمٍ يَطْعَمُهُ إِلَّا أَن يَكُونَ مَيْتَةً أَوْ دَمًا مَسْفُوحًا أَوْ لَحْمَ خِنْزِيرٍ"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to degust, to taste"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to insert, to inoculate, to graft, to introduce","examples":[{"text":"قال يونيوس يطعم الأترج كتطعيم الكرم وتطاعم التوت في الأترج والأترج في التفاح والتفاح في الأترج ويكون التفاح أحمر بالطبع إن ركب في شجر الدلب والقراسيا يحب التطعيم ويطعم في كرمة","english":"Junius said that the citron can be inoculated into the vine, and the mulberry into the citron, and the citron into the apple, and the apple into the citron, and the apple is naturally incarned if grafted onto the plane, and the cherry loves inoculation and can be inoculated into a vine."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to put bait on"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of طَعِمَ (ṭaʕima) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"taste, flavor","examples":[{"text":"مَثَلُ الْجَنَّةِ ٱلَّتِي وُعِدَ ٱلْمُتَّقُونَ ۖ فِيهَا أَنْهَارٌ مِن مَاءٍ غَيْرِ آسِنٍ وَأَنْهَارٌ مِن لَبَنٍ لَمْ يَتَغَيَّرْ طَعْمُهُ وَأَنْهَارٌ مِنْ خَمْرٍ لَذَّةٍ لِلشَّارِبِينَ وَأَنْهَارٌ مِنْ عَسَلٍ مُّصَفًّى ۖ وَلَهُمْ فِيهَا مِنْ كُلِّ ٱلثَّمَرَاتِ وَمَغْفِرَةٌ مِّنْ رَبِّهِمْ ۖ كَمَنْ هُوَ خَالِدٌ فِي النَّارِ وَسُقُوا مَاءً حَمِيمًا فَقَطَّعَ أَمْعَاءَهُمْ"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"morsel of food, chunk"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pith pulp, medulla; serum, lymph"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"truncheon for grafting"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"bait for hunting"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of طُعْمَة (ṭuʕma)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ط ع م (ṭ ʕ m). Cognate with Hebrew טַעַם (ta'am), Amharic ጣዕም (t’a'em)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26732","headword_ar":"طَعْمٌ","root":"TEm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[as an inf. n.: see 1. ―         -b2-  As a simple subst.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Taste, flavour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"savour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sweetness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bitterness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a quality"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of any kind"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between these two,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in food and in beverage: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuEuwmN","text_ar":"طُعُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaEomuhu mur~N","text_ar":"طَعْمُهُ مُرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Its taste is bitter"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HulowN","text_ar":"حُلْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sweet"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (Msb, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAmiDN","text_ar":"حَامِضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acid"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tagay~ara TaEomuhu","text_ar":"تَغَيَّرَ طَعْمُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Its taste became altered from its natural quality."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b3-  And ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Relish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a desired quality"},{"kind":"text","text":"of food. (S, Msb, K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layosa lahu TaEomN","text_ar":"لَيْسَ لَهُ طَعْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It has no relish"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layosa lilogav~i","text_ar":"لَيْسَ لِلْغَثِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is lean has no relish"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaEamN","text_ar":"طَعَمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same in the dial. of Kiláb. (Msb.) ―         -b4-  [Hence, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An approvable quality"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a man.] One says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN *uw TaEomN","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ ذُو طَعْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man possessing intelligence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prudence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discretion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA","text_ar":"مَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bifulaAnK TaEomN walaA nawiySN","text_ar":"بِفُلَانٍ طَعْمٌ وَلَا نَوِيصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is not in such a one intelligence nor activity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layosa limaA yafoEalu","text_ar":"لَيْسَ لِمَا يَفْعَلُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN TaEomN","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ طَعْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There appertains not to what such a one does any pleasing quality, nor any place of honour in the heart,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and it is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA qatalonaA A^aHadFA bihi TaEomN maA qatalonaA A_il~aA EajaAy^iza SuloEFA","text_ar":"مَا قَتَلْنَا اَحَدًا بِهِ طَعْمٌ مَا قَتَلْنَا اـِلَّا عَجَايِزَ صُلْعًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We slew not any one of account, any known person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any one of rank,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"station;"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"we slew not any but bald-headed old women;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and one may also say in this case ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuEomN","text_ar":"طُعْمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm. (TA.) ―         -b5-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing that is swallowed easily"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"agreeably,"},{"kind":"text","text":"whether"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"solid, as grains"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c."},{"kind":"text","text":"], or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"liquid, as expressed juice"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"oil"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vinegar"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c."},{"kind":"text","text":"]; differing from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuEomN","text_ar":"طُعْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which does not apply to liquids. (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["S","TA","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n26733","headword_ar":"طُعْمٌ","root":"TEm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[as an inf. n.: see 1: ―         -b2- ] as a subst.: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaEaAmN","text_ar":"طَعَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Grain that is thrown to birds."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, Msb, TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A bait that is thrown to fish."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaEaAmu TuEomK","text_ar":"طَعَامُ طُعْمٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Food that satisfies the stomach of its eater:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISh, K, TA:) and is said by MF to be for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaEaAmu $aYo'K TuEomK","text_ar":"طَعَامُ شَىْءٍ طُعْمٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) The Prophet said of the well Zemzem,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahaA TaEaAmu TuEomK","text_ar":"اـِنَّهَا طَعَامُ طُعْمٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily it is a satisfier of the stomach of man,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISh, Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like as is food."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaEomN","text_ar":"طَعْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["ISh","K","TA","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n26734","headword_ar":"طَعَمٌ","root":"TEm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"; see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaEomN","text_ar":"طَعْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n26735","headword_ar":"طَعِمٌ","root":"TEm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAEimN","text_ar":"طَاعِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}